 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EFairChance develops a micro-lottery system to be used at online and physical point-of-sales. FairChance\u0026#8217;s idea is that a consumer in the checkout process of physical or electronic stores would add a FairChance lottery ticket into the purchase, and get a chance of winning e.g. their shopping basket for free. Fair Chance\u0026#8217;s leading idea is to support charities like Red Cross, Right To Play, Diambars, and Save the Children. FairChance\u0026#8217;s service offers new income to retailers, and new type of fund raising and promotion to charity and humanitarian organizations.\u003C/p\u003E",
